---
const values = [
  {
    number: "01",
    title: "No Generic Advice",
    description: "Every situation is unique. You get strategies tailored to your personality, your goals, and the specific woman you're interested in."
  },
  {
    number: "02",
    title: "Real-World Results",
    description: "Theory means nothing without action. Every session is designed to give you practical moves you can execute tonight."
  },
  {
    number: "03",
    title: "Brutal Honesty",
    description: "No sugar-coating. No feel-good nonsense. You'll hear exactly what you need to hear — and that's why it works."
  }
];
---

<section class="relative pt-8 pb-16 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-bg via-bg-card/30 to-bg"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left side -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="text-[#ff087b] text-base font-normal tracking-[0.15em] uppercase">Why We?</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mt-4 leading-none tracking-tight">
          BECAUSE WE CAN<br />
          <span class="text-[#ff087b]">BECAUSE YOU DESERVE MORE</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-4 leading-relaxed max-w-lg" style="font-weight: 500;">
          Most men struggle in communication with women because they don't realize there's another way. We are here to show you a different side — where confidence feels natural, attraction requires no effort, and every woman you meet can feel your energy and fall in love with you.<br /><br />
          We have powerful tools and creativity to attract any woman.<br />
          We serve love and your smile — and we do it beautifully, with pleasure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right side -->
      <div class="space-y-6 reveal reveal-delay-2">
        {values.map((val) => (
          <div class="group p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-bg-card/50 hover:bg-bg-card-hover hover:border-accent/20 transition-all duration-500 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent/40 text-5xl font-black group-hover:text-accent/60 transition-colors duration-500 leading-none">{val.number}</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">{val.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-white/80 transition-colors duration-300">{val.description}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
